commit message:
Package Rename

Renamed the entire project to a new, and shorter, name to be able to
publish to Google Play.

Update AndroidManifest Package Name

Updated the Android Manifest file's package name to match the new
package names.

Package Name Issue

Fixed the auto-generated resource package name reference.

Minor Version Increment

Incremented the version slightly to allow for the fixed version to be
upload onto Google Play.
